author: ehatcher
msg: Simplify schema, with only 4 fields: id, text, *_facet, and *_text.  The client does not send text, only *_text, which gets copied into the text field.  This is surely overly simplified, and will evolve back as field name munging facilities are added and other data types are supported.

author: ehatcher
msg: Modeled Solr's StandardRequestHandler (qt=standard) as Solr::Request::Standard (includes common, standard, and facet parameters, but not  highlighting parameters).
